t exported from `src/index.ts`, making it inaccessible in the container's dist bundle. Added re-export to `src/index.ts` and rebuilt.\n- **ESM import workaround:** Container requires `VITEST=1` env var to suppress CLI auto-parse on module import. Uses `node --input-type=module` for ESM.\n- **[OBSERVABILITY GAP]** VictoriaLogs returned zero log events for all parser invocations — `parseStreamLine` is a pure function with no telemetry.\n- **Non-standard status from previous session:** Sprint status had `verified` (not a valid status). Normalized to `verifying` before proceeding.\n- All 6 ACs passed black-box verification after infrastructure fix.\n\n---\n\n## Session 2 — Started 2026-03-21T10:44Z\n\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":858,"cache_read_input_tokens":37229,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":858},"output_tokens":25,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"3e8c45fc-a757-4d77-9a55-f32a41bfdb65","uuid":"ce5b8452-480a-4260-a958-914a21bf24f7"}
