{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01S5bHdDx6vt5aahqj71ACRd","type":"tool_result","content":"   190→\n   191→Running in background. Check progress:\n   192→  → codeharness status          (one-screen summary)\n   193→  → codeharness run --live      (streaming output)\n   194→  → codeharness run --stop      (graceful stop after current story)\n   195→```\n   196→\n   197→### Live Mode: `codeharness run --live`\n   198→\n   199→Rolling status that updates in place:\n   200→\n   201→```\n   202→$ codeharness run --live\n   203→\n   204→codeharness run | iteration 3 | 47m elapsed | $12.30 spent\n   205→━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n   206→Story: 3-2-bmad-installation-workflow-patching\n   207→Phase: verify → AC 8/12 (docker exec ... codeharness init --json)\n   208→\n   209→Done: 3-1 ✓  4-1 ✓  4-2 ✓\n   210→This: 3-2 ◆ verifying (8/12 ACs)\n   211→Next: 3-3 (verifying, no proof yet)\n   212→\n   213→Blocked: 0-1 ✕ (10/10)  13-3 ✕ (10/10)\n   214→━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n   215→```\n   216→\n   217→### Story Completes\n   218→\n   219→```\n   220→[OK] Story 3-2: DONE — 12/12 ACs verified\n   221→  └ Proof: verification/3-2-proof.md\n   222→  └ Duration: 18m | Cost: $4.20\n   223→[INFO] Sprint: 18/65 done (28%) — moving to 3-3\n   224→```\n   225→\n   226→### Story Returned to Dev\n   227→\n   228→```\n   229→[WARN] Story 3-3: verification found 2 failing ACs → returning to dev\n   230→  └ AC 3: bridge --dry-run output missing epic headers\n   231→  └ AC 7: bridge creates duplicate beads issues\n   232→  └ Attempt 2/10 — dev will fix and re-verify\n   233→```\n   234→\n   235→### Story Failed\n   236→\n   237→```\n   238→[FAIL] Story 2-3: verification failed at AC 4 (attempt 3/10)\n   239→  └ docker exec codeharness-verify codeharness status --check-docker → exit 1\n   240→  └ Output: \"[FAIL] VictoriaMetrics stack: not running\"\n   241→  └ Returning to dev for fix 