{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01Bsb28nRTD1Fdcms8kgSkVW","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01YBFoxXyPLM5jdTeehnQbbq","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/.session-issues.md","old_string":"- **Observation:** Old `epic-6-retrospective.md` documents Brownfield Onboarding epic, not Dashboard Visualization Rework — stale/misleading.","new_string":"- **Observation:** Old `epic-6-retrospective.md` documents Brownfield Onboarding epic, not Dashboard Visualization Rework — stale/misleading.\n\n### 6-1-rewrite-ink-components-match-ux-spec — dev-story (2026-03-21T10:56Z)\n\n- **Workaround: file split to avoid circular imports** — NFR9 300-line limit forced a 3-file split. `ink-app.tsx` composes `ink-components.tsx` and `ink-activity-components.tsx` to avoid circular deps. Adds indirection.\n- **Cost accumulation edge case** — `result` event cost only accumulates when `state.sprintInfo` is non-null. Cost from early events before sprint state init is lost.\n- **Iteration count delay** — `currentIterationCount` in run.ts is a mutable closure variable, updated from stderr parsing. Iteration count updates are delayed until next 5-second polling interval.\n- **Missing artifacts** — AGENTS.md, exec-plan, and proof document not created (not in story tasks)."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1454,"cache_read_input_tokens":42146,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1454},"output_tokens":25,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"3e8c45fc-a757-4d77-9a55-f32a41bfdb65","uuid":"099e7afe-93bb-416a-a6e9-988098c10ef9"}
