{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_016DaidaQrW1kSEYqp4qp5fi","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01L994BdaLiV2q12xM61qQ7K","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/.session-issues.md","old_string":"- **Missing artifacts** — AGENTS.md, exec-plan, and proof document not created (not in story tasks).","new_string":"- **Missing artifacts** — AGENTS.md, exec-plan, and proof document not created (not in story tasks).\n\n### 6-1-rewrite-ink-components-match-ux-spec — code-review (2026-03-21T11:01Z)\n\n- **HIGH bug fixed:** `updateSprintState()` wiped accumulated `totalCost` every 5s during polling — cost display would flash and disappear. Fixed with field preservation.\n- **MEDIUM bug fixed:** `startsWith` key comparison in `StoryBreakdown` caused false matches (e.g., story `3-2` matching `3-20`). Fixed to exact comparison.\n- **LOW unfixed:** `run.ts` is 308 lines (8 over NFR9 300-line limit). Pre-existing.\n- **Coverage gap:** No integration test for full run→renderer→component pipeline with cost accumulation across polling cycles.\n- **Architecture concern:** Renderer accumulates cost internally with no external read path. `updateSprintState` has implicit merge behavior."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1518,"cache_read_input_tokens":45051,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1518},"output_tokens":24,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"3e8c45fc-a757-4d77-9a55-f32a41bfdb65","uuid":"f6823458-cdaa-4bce-80a0-9305a053edcb"}
